@page "/Ranges"

<h1><span class="oi oi-headphones" aria-hidden="true"></span>&nbsp;Ranges</h1>
There are several ranges at Lonestar Range & Academy. Tap below to get information on distances and calibers allowed on each.

<br/><br/>

<div class="text-center">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('pistol').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Pistol</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('rifle').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Rifle</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('shotgun').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Shotgun</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('training').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Training</button>
</div>

<br/><br/>

<h2 id="pistol">Pistol</h2>
<img src="range_pistol.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Pistol Range" /><br/>

<p>
The pistol range offers a 3 yard, 7 yard and 15 yard range allowing pistols, revolvers and pistol carbines to be shot.

<ul class="list-group">
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active">
    Common Calibers Allowed
  </li>

  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">22</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">38 Special</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">380</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">9mm</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">40 S&W</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">45 ACP</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">10mm</li>
</ul>
</p>

<h2 id="rifle">Rifle</h2>
<img src="range_rifle.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Rifle Range" /><br/>

<p>
The rifle range offers a 25 yard, 50/100 yard and two 100 yard bays.<br />

Spotting scopes are available in the office.

<ul class="list-group">
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active">
    Common Calibers Allowed
  </li>

  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">22LR</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">.223</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">.30-06</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">5.56x45</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">6.5 Creedmoor</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">7.62x39</li>
  <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">7.62x51/.308</li>
</ul>
</p>

